    <title>第一篇博客</title>
    <url>/2024/07/09/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo的基本设置与操作流程"><a href="#hexo的基本设置与操作流程" class="headerlink" title="hexo的基本设置与操作流程"></a>hexo的基本设置与操作流程</h1><h2 id="基本设置"><a href="#基本设置" class="headerlink" title="基本设置"></a>基本设置</h2><ol>
<li>更改主题<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#_config.yml
theme:xxx<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>
<li>更改默认布局为草稿(draft)<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#_config.yml
default_layout: draft<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="操作流程"><a href="#操作流程" class="headerlink" title="操作流程"></a>操作流程</h2><ol>
<li>新建草稿<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo new &quot;文件名&quot;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>
<li>编辑<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#source&#x2F;draft&#x2F;文件名.md<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>
<li>移动草稿到要发布的文章类别中<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo publish &quot;file&quot;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>
<li>文章生成<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo g<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>
<li>blog本地预览<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo s<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>
<li>blog 更新到网络<pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo d<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>
</ol>
]]></content>
